Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:05.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An average man, Kaiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:07.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日々 怠惰で自堕落な生活を\N送っていた平凡な男 カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,who lives a life of sloth and self-indulgence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One day, suddenly, he is thrust deep into debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのカイジに ある日突然\N借金が降りかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:14.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,due to having cosigned a friend's loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間の保証人になったことが\N原因だった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:20.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To win forgiveness of that debt, he boards the Ship of Hope, Espoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金をチャラにするため\N乗り込んだのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:21.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の船 ｢エスポワール｣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is invited to an evening with the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:26.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは悪魔の夜へと誘われる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罠 裏切り だまし合い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:29.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Traps! Betrayals! Cheats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,繰り広げられる狂気のギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:33.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate gamble unfolds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:39.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして幾多の困難を乗り越え\Nカイジは たどり着く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:39.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And Kaiji survives through it, to face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:46.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The demon of the underworld and Teiai's CEO, Kazutaka Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,闇の世界に君臨する魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛グループの総帥 兵藤和尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:55.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは負けるべくして負け\N兵藤は勝つべくして勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:54.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, fated to lose, loses. Hyodo, fated to win, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:01:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは王の王たる所以を\N手痛い代償を払い 思い知らされる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:01:01.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, defeated by the King, is held to his debt. {dongs fuck this like there's three of us and NONE of us agree}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:08.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thus, the devil's night was sealed with Kaiji's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:06.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして悪魔の夜に\Nようやく終止符が打たれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:08.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの血によって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And as the seasons change!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして季節が流れ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ なんで出ねえんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is he!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何してくれてんだ オラ！\Nやべっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:24.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:25.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれから数ヵ月　カイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Several months have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:36.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is once again living a life of sloth and self-indulgence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらず\N怠惰で自堕落な生活を送っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 兵藤に敗れた時点での\Nカイジの借金は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:41.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But when Kaiji lost to Hyodo, his debt was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,668万
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:43.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,6.8 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:50.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Further, treatment of his ear and fingers at an underground clinic cost another two million!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに闇医者による\N指と耳の縫合手術の入院で200万
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:55.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With interest factored in, his debts have reached 9.5 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後 それに金利が加わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:56.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金は膨らみ950万
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに数日前から帝愛グループに\N追われる身となった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:00.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Teiai Group has been in pursuit of him for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji does not yet know this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがカイジは\Nそのことをまだ知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:07.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn that walking trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:08.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:10.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh, who had entered Kaiji in both
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに限定ジャンケンと\N人間競馬を斡旋した 遠藤は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Restricted Rock, Paper, Scissors and the Human Derby,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川の失脚後\Nメーンの仕事を外され
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,after his failure lost his usual position
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:21.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and was assigned to finding and "recovering" defaulted debtors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失踪した劣悪債務者の捜査と\N取り立ての仕事をしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラッキー！\N迎えに来てくれたんすね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:47.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Great! You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？\N俺 金に困ってましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda broke right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even be able to make the hundred thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:55.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃあ借金1000万なんて\N逆立ちしたって返せねえんすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,if you turned me upside down and shook me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 何でもやりますから\N紹介してくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:00.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything! Just show me where the action is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが！\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:08.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So, how are your ear and your fingers feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 耳と指いかれてんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今度は絶対 勝ちますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time I'll win! I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 自信があんだ　ほんとっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけの痛手を負って\Nまだ懲りずにギャンブルだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's still trying to gamble after he went through that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought he was better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちったあ\Nまともな奴かと思ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's sad. He's a total junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,哀れな 悲しいほどの\Nジャンキーぶりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全にいかれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Completely nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついてこい\Nさすが遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come through, Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:46.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time I'm really gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん 俺 今度こそ\N絶対勝ってみせますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:52.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. There is no winning or losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 ありゃしねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つも負けるも\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,睡眠剤だ\Nしばらく眠ってもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That should knock you out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to me, you bastard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様… どうす… る気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:14.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going to work, you loan cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働くんだよ　劣悪債務者はな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？働くって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Work...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:21.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… まあまあ\Nそれは起きた時のお楽しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll find out all about that when you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは… 一体 どんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな　地獄さ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In Hell. Deep underground, just like it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文字通りの地の獄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:38.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you owe about ten million, so it'll take you fifteen years or so to pay it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の借金は\Nほぼ1000万だから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ 15年は入ってもらう計算か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じ… 15？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fif...teen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　15年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降ろせ　降ろへ… 降ろへー…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let... me out... Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降ろひまへん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけばカイジは地の獄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji awakens in the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An unknown location, deep in the bowels of the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:04.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこか分からぬ地中の底の底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:08.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異様な熱気と騒音\N粉塵 悪臭 不衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hot and loud... Dusty, smelly, and unsafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A forced labor camp of the disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亡者巣くう強制労働の施設にいた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この工事は帝愛の幹部たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:19.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is not only Teiai's nuclear shelter, but an entire underground kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,核シェルターを兼ねた\N超豪勢な地下王国造り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この劣悪な環境下で\N働かされている者は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like Kaiji, forced to labor after his default,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 カイジと同じ\N多額な負債を背負い確保された者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the other workers also bear deep debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:32.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ\N(笛の音)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:35.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作業終了！各班ごとに整列
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shift over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Line up by group!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:39.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと並べ！Ａ班 Ｂ班 行進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A group and B group, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:45.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作業が終わると脱衣\Nそして シャワー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:45.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When their work is finished, they strip and shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That fucker tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ ふざけやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:55.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ！\Nおい 早くしてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then they eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:06:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして食事\Nおかずは メザシとたくわんだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their repast is nothing but dried sardines and pickled radish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貧しい食事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A mere pittance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When this is finished, they return to their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが終わると部屋に戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is E group's barracks, home to 23 men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこはＥ班23人の相部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:13.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Inside are old newspapers, old magazines, shogi and go boards, and cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:13.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのは古雑誌と古新聞\N将棋 囲碁 トランプの類い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:18.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Night and day spent with one's comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:18.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四六時中 仲間と一緒\N朝も昼も夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:22.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:26.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Woken at 5AM by an alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,朝５時 サイレンの音に\N叩き起こされ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:29.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部屋の掃除 朝食の後 作業開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,they clean their room, eat breakfast, and return to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Apart from a short break for lunch, they work until evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昼食を挟み 夕方まで働かされる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毎日が その繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The daily routine never changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:39.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji must work 15 years in this hidden underground society,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは地上と完全に隔離された\Nこの地下社会で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:43.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,cut off from all contact with the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:43.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,15年 働き続けなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ 地上で逃げ回ってる方が\Nよっぽどマシだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:47.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit... Even just being chased around on the outside would beat this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 脱走しようにも\N監視カメラが常に見張っている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if I try to escape, the security cameras will catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:57.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if I fool the cameras and break down that thick door,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮にあのカメラをごまかして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分厚いドアの向こうに\N出たとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その先は\N複雑に入り組んだ巨大迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,nothing lies beyond but a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is an inescapable underground fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:04.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出不可能な地下要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは 看守辺りを\N人質にとって脱出しようにも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And even if I take a supervisor hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各班長はもちろん\N工事長に至るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:13.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All the foremen, even the director, are down here because they didn't pay their debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 借金をカタに連れてこられた\N言うなら囚人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:17.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're all prisoners. Useless to ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人質の意味を成さない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員で反乱する手もあるが\Nそれはどうもありそうにない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like rioting would do the trick, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not only are the guards strict,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほどひどい環境にありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,there's enough of a hierarchy established to hold things down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:29.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一種のヒエラルキーの下\N妙に秩序立っている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So my only hope is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば 唯一の希望は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勤労奨励オプション
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The hard work bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A one-day vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日外出券
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,囚人たちの労働意欲高揚のために\N設けた超特例措置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In order to encourage the prisoners to work harder,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,special incentives are offered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:47.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One of those is this one-day vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:47.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがこの１日外出券
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All I need for that is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金さえ出せば あれが手に入る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく１日でも外へ出れば\N何とかなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I can just get out of here for one day, I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外にさえ行けば\N競馬や競輪 裏カジノ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I'm out, I can make it to a track, or an illegal casino...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいい　何でもいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anything! Anything would work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でも１発 当てさえすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:07.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just one win, and I'll pay that ten million back all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:08.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万ぽっちの借金 屁でもねえ\N叩き返せる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万ペリカ\N１日外出券を得るには
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It costs 500,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:16.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My ticket out of here for a day is 500,000 perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,注目ー！\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Great work out there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日も作業 ご苦労さまでした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,労働手帳に今日の分のハンコを\N押しておきました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've signed your timecards for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お返しします　それと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll pass them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, and it's finally payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はお待ちかね 給料日でーす！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come up and take your pay when I call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:41.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前を呼ばれたら\N順番に取りに来てください
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His first payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初給料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,91,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９万1000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:50.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,perica are a currency used only in this underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペリカとはこの地下社会だけで\N通用する貨幣単位のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:58.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their value is 1/10 that of the yen; that is, 91,000 perica is worth 9,100 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その価値 日本円の10分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり９万1000ペリカは\N9100円ということになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ヵ月 筆舌に\N尽くしがたい重労働に耐え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:02.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In return for a month of backbreaking labor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずか9100円
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji receives only 9,100 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's debt is 9.5 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの借金は950万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:10.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利息だけで月14万ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The interest alone is nearly 140,000 yen a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無職のカイジには\N利息からして支払い不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:14.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, with no job, cannot pay even the interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:18.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But working underground, that usurious interest is forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしこの地下で働くならば\Nその重い金利はチャラ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:23.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bit by bit, he can begin to pay down that 9.5 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:23.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかずつだが 借金の元金\N950万を減らしていける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:29.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji's daily wage is only 3,500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが１日働いて支払われる日当は\N日本円で3500円
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このうち2000円が\N借金の返済に充てられ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of that, 2,000 yen is applied to his debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに1150円が 食費や\N施設利用費などの名目で消える
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:38.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another 1,150 yen are taken to pay for room and board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He receives only a scant tenth of the original 3,500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手にするのは3500円の10分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For a day's labor, only 350 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日働いて たったの350円
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn it! This is just insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ ふざけやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:51.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Meaning everything rests on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ\Nこれに全てが懸かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's entire future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの未来 行く末が！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にもビール\Nはい 5000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me a beer, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, that'll be 5,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 俺にも！\N俺 ロング缶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have a tallboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 6000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,6,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ポテトチップも\Nはいはい　合計9000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And some chips too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, that'll be 9,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have some nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は柿ピーね\Nはいはい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが！欲に流れて\N夢も追えないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're throwing away their dreams! Those greedy idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自堕落な連中め！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,5,000 perica for a beer? That's 500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビール１本5000ペリカ\N500円だぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外の倍以上の値段だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's more than twice what it costs outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな調子で使ったら\Nあっという間にこんな金 消し飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:22.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll blow all their money in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:29.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no saving people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに こいつらときたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えねえ　クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm different. I'll save.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は違う　俺は貯める
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At 91,000 perica a month, if I save up for 6 months...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このひと月９万のペリカを\N６ヵ月貯めれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,54万ペリカ　あの外出券に届く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's 540,000 perica! I'll be able to afford my ticket out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:42.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,届くんだ！となりゃ 誰が使うか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would blow their money with that dangling in front of their faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使うか！クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:51.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 頑なになればなるほど\Nその反動は大きい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:51.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But as determined as Kaiji is, he faces stiff opposition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:05.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても 何なんだ\Nこの胸のざわめきは？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:05.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It makes perfect sense! So why am I so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… そうよ 買える\N俺は買える
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know! I can buy something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll buy something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've had nothing all month!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入ってひと月は\Nどうにもならなかったが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の俺なら買える
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can afford to buy things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Smokes! Chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タバコ ポテチ\N缶コーヒー 焼き鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Coffee! Yakitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビールも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:30.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:35.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… 分かるよ カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… 班長\N外出券だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Foreman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:42.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I used to think I'd go for the ticket out of here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えることは一緒だ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも最初 そうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna spend a single yen here, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となりゃー こんな所で\N使っちゃいられねえよなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you can't deprive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 無理はいけねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:52.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理は続かない\N自分を適度に許すことが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:54.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never last if you try to fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長続きのコツさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\Nわしのおごりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:12:00.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, my treat. Let's celebrate your first payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の初給料のお祝いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No need to pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金は取らねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Foreman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ！\Nキンキンに冷えてやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… ありがてえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:20.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I'm crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,涙が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯罪的だ！うますぎる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:36.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This should be a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's fucking tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,労働の火照りと部屋の熱気で\N息苦しい体に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:43.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My first beer after suffering a month through the heat and the sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ヵ月ぶりのビール！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,染み込んできやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I feel it flowing through my veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体に…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,溶けそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ ビール１本のためなら\N強盗だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:06.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I have to beg, borrow, or steal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… あんなもので\Nビール飲めたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just one more beer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… クソーッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Dammit!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:32.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 買おうと思えば\N買えなくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:31.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, there's nothing wrong with buying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:37.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I earn 90,000 perica a month, that's 540,000 perica in half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:37.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ヵ月の給料が９万ペリカ\N６ヵ月貯めれば54万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日外出券の50万ペリカに届く
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ticket out of here is only 500,000 perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは ４万余分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I'm 40,000 over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:45.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have spare money! And if I have money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余るってことだ　その気になれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ　ダメだ\N６ヵ月でたったの４万だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's only 40,000 and it has to last me half a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使うのは よっぽど特別な時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to save it for special occasions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特別な日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えろ　耐えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll endure! I must endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:03.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji endures! Endures desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 耐える　必死に 耐える\Nだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We've already got him over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一段落ついたな\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hi, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい はい はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？何なの？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What can I get for you, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:18.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…だけ\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:20.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１本…\N１本？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１本ってそれ ビールかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビール350を１本ってことかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A twelve-ounce can of beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One beer for Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい カイジ君\Nビール お買い上げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just one is okay. I've endured a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１本はいい\N考えてみれば１ヵ月はガマンした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は特別な日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here you go, nice and chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい どうぞ　冷えてるよ\Nで つまみは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about a snack to go with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は？\Nせっかく飲むんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:47.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You haven't had a drink in ages. It's a waste to just have one beer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビールだけって 味気ないって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまもうよ　何でもいいからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get a snack. We've got anything you'd want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then... How about those nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ そこの柿ピ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ヘタだな カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not any good at this, are you, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nヘタッピさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲望の解放のさせ方がヘタ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You need to learn how to let yourself loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が本当に欲しいのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ　これをチンして\Nホッカホカにしてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A nice hot snack to go with your cold beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷えたビールでやりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ　だけどそれは\Nあまりに値が張るから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:24.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But they're out of your price range, so you're settling for these sorry nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちのショボい柿ピーで\Nごまかそうっていうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't do that to yourself, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 ダメなんだよ それじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:31.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく冷えたビールで\Nスカッとしようって時に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:33.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Having those with a nice cold beer will just stress you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃ\Nかえってストレスが溜まる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:38.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll be too worried about the chicken you could've had to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食えなかった焼き鳥が\Nちらついてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然スッキリしない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の毒は残ったままだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You just won't be able to let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜいたくってやつはさ\N小出しじゃダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:45.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're going to indulge yourself, you need to go all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる時ゃ きっちりやった方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When you go for it, really go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ次の節制の\N励みになるってもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:51.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to encourage yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now c'mon, give yourself a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分へのご褒美さ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われてみれば確かにそうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:57.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ…\Nはい 焼き鳥 お買い上げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One order of yakitori, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１分 お待ちください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実はポテチも…\Nはい ポテチもお買い上げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'd like some chips too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Potato chips too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:11.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're having that much you're gonna need another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると ビール１本じゃ\N全然 足りないよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:28.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うー 最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:31.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも貧しい食事ばっかだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Compared to those terrible rations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,this convenience store yakitori and nikujaga just sticks to the ribs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなコンビニの焼き鳥や\N肉じゃがが染みる… 染みる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:39.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くーっ！ってビールが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:47.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッフッフ…\Nバカ丸出しですね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The idiot's going all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカだからね あんなもんよ\N今の若いもんなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:51.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's because he's an idiot. Kids these days are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:55.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once he's full and happy, he'll say this to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べ終わったら 奴はとりあえず\N満足してこう考えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,"I'll work harder tomorrow. I'll start saving tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:59.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢明日から頑張ろう｣\N｢明日から節約だ｣と
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But that's not a good way to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ その考え方がダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日から頑張るんじゃない\N今日　今日だけ頑張るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:07.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't work harder tomorrow. You work harder today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those who work hard today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:10.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日を頑張った者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:14.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日を頑張り始めた者にのみ\N明日が来るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:14.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those who work hard today are the only ones who have a tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また１人 確保ってことですね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So he's gonna be here for a while, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　ってことになるな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This food is the only pleasure we're allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:23.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにはこの｢食｣以外\N他に快楽がない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So its temptation is extremely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:26.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆえに その誘惑は強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once you fall for it once, you're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:29.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 知ったらもう抗えない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:31.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局のところ\N｢ちょっと１杯｣ってのが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:33.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a fool if you think you'll just have one on special occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大甘なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:40.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And that one can is your first step on your tumble into this abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その１杯がこの底辺のさらに底辺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,底の底へ転がり落ちる最初の一歩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入り口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A one-way entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてカイジ 豪遊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:48.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji goes wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４万1000ペリカの散財！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He blows 41,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　結局のところ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are only two kinds of people:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:18:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中は利用する側とされる側\Nその２種類しかいないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those who use and those who are used!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The only question is the obvious—when will he realize!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:05.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は その当たり前に\Nいつ気づくかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(笛の音)\N作業終了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shift over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい ビールお待ち\Nはい 毎度どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One beer, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちら5000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That'll be 5,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ 座禅組んで\N欲望の火が消えりゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:25.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Trying Zen meditation to stave off his desires? I guess that works for a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も苦労しねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I give him about 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ 持って30分ってとこか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:32.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji contemplates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:32.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 反省！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！この状況から\N６ヵ月で50万貯めるとなると
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:39.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I want to get out of here in six months, I can't spend any more money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使える金は もうない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:44.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ給料の端数の\N1000や2000は使えなくもないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I could spend the extra 1000s from my pay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６ヵ月 何にも使えないなんて\Nいや というより
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't stand not buying anything for a whole month...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:55.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've already blown my plan not to spend any more than 40,000 over six months!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと６ヵ月で\N４万しか使えないという計画に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理があったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７ヵ月？そうだ ７ヵ月にすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I take seven months?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it! If I take seven months I'll be able to reach 500,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理なく50万に届く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら 少しはいいか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I can indulge myself just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい カイジ君\Nビール お買い上げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One beer for Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One beer, coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビール１本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば 豪遊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When Kaiji came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He realized he had gone wild again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２日 続けて豪遊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For the second time in as many days!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またやってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:29.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 猛省！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:28.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji searches his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:33.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But even as he does so, he spends more and more over the next two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 猛省しつつも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翌日 翌々日とチビチビ使い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And on the fifth day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:39.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして５日目 残金400ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has only 400 perica left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has arrived at the tearful conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに来たトホホな状況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:46.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can buy only twelve peanuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:46.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買えるのは ばら売りの柿ピー\N３粒100ペリカを４回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,給料日まで25日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:53.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There are 25 days left until payday! Can his desires be sated with half a peanut a day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜいたくは柿ピー１日\N半かけらという計算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:01.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki, the foreman, makes his next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:01.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして班長の大槻は次の手に出る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wanna borrow some cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借りる？\N給料の前借りさ　わしが請け負う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:07.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll give you an advance on your pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし そんなことしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:13.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあに 借りて 今度こそ\N無理なく使っていけばいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:13.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You really should go ahead and borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:19.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you're just going to be depriving yourself until next payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし借りなきゃ カイジ君は\N次の給料日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,禁欲生活ってことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not good for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:22.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その禁欲ってのがよくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, this is a rubber ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 心はゴムだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押さえつければ\N必ず跳ね返そうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Press it, and it springs back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:35.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Meaning... If you try to hold yourself back, you'll just blow it all the moment you get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:33.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり いくら頑張っても\N給料が入ると その禁欲の反動で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また豪遊してしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうもんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより今 ６もらってだな\N６？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So how about borrowing sixty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sixty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an advance, so it's not like I can give you the whole ninety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前借りだからね\N９万全部ってわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ相応の手数料を\Nもらわないとね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:48.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There needs to be something in it for me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What if they move one of us to a different group?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:53.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突然の配置換えがあったり\N貸した相手に寝込まれたりと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:57.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or if you just quit working or something. I'm taking a risk too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構 こっちには\N取りっぱぐれのリスクがあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ６ってのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But sixty is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:03.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ 足りないのは\N自分で補えばいいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:03.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't think it's enough, you can always earn some more for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,噂じゃカイジ君は\N相当の腕だって聞いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:07.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've heard you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:12.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about it? Why not get back to your old habits tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:12.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだい？今夜辺り\Nこいつで復活っていうのは？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A devil beckons in the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底の底で悪魔が誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイコロ賭博 チンチロリン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:25.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dice game chinchirorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just one win,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:46.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think of this an an anime, I think of it as a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:50.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I put all of my energy into each performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:57.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:11.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
